# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baiparkdate.rpy:33
translate french baiparkstartdate_4053ffc0:

    # "Bai and I walk around the trails, chit-chatting for a while."
    "Bai et moi, on se promène sur les sentiers en bavardant un moment."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baiparkdate.rpy:44
translate french baiparkstartdate_236ab045:

    # "Eventually, we reach the bench halfway along the trail."
    "Finalement, on arrive au banc situé à mi-chemin du sentier."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baiparkdate.rpy:52
translate french baiparkstartdate_1b78059e:

    # "We sit next to each other for a bit, chatting."
    "On s’assoit l’un à côté de l’autre un moment, en discutant."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baiparkdate.rpy:54
translate french baiparkstartdate_8ab96ed5:

    # "I'm still a little uncomfortable with this, and I'm pretty sure he is too."
    "Je me sens encore un peu mal à l’aise, et je suis presque sûr que lui aussi."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baiparkdate.rpy:55
translate french baiparkstartdate_96695859:

    # "Things are a little awkward."
    "L'ambiance est un peu gênante."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baiparkdate.rpy:58
translate french baiparkstartdate_fbccb841:

    # "I put my arm around him and we sit in a comfortable silence together, just enjoying being close."
    "Je passe mon bras autour de lui et on reste assis ensemble dans un silence confortable, profitant simplement d'être proches."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baiparkdate.rpy:59
translate french baiparkstartdate_cf2869ab:

    # "Then, after a while, it's time to head back."
    "Puis, au bout d'un moment, il est temps de rentrer."

